{"tid":2200760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：八國聯軍結集，香港人不能置身事外了，因為2016年，香港人放棄了陳雲。","createTime":"2020-09-13T08:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T08:18:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"85424478cf393189238c7b9119522d7747e52dc3","tid":2200760,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjyshw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwjyshw8.jpg&h=30493ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳雲：看著日本、英國、德國、澳洲等國趕忙加入美國發起的印太聯盟，就感受到往日清朝文人見到八國聯軍結集天津的滋味。 <br />\n五口通商，利益均霑，洋人租界，蒙藏獨立，這些東西，又要降臨在華夏的土地上了。<br />\n（我們不能以香港人來置身事外了，因為2016年，香港人放棄了陳雲賜予香港人置身事外的機會，放棄香港大都會的天下觀，竟然擁抱親共文人毒害香港的香港民族論，現在香港大要與中國共存亡了。香港人，比陳雲還要愛中國。陳雲沒辦法了。）"},{"pid":"1da93be4c0dc521662b197f967a7d4eaa95d416c","tid":2200760,"uid":299436,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"想知以前支持佢嘅人而家有幾多頂唔順佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104fe79e07457c7ddfb5336c6c31c4e8e7f10aea","tid":2200760,"uid":41974,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"1da93be4c0dc521662b197f967a7d4eaa95d416c","tid":2200760,"uid":299436,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"想知以前支持佢嘅人而家有幾多頂唔順佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"我..."},{"pid":"029a08361e2d05f5724c7f161ce5f5979c55463d","tid":2200760,"uid":254788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"又發咩撚野癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01130f142d6d2b317e6774afb3b0765f9e263156","tid":2200760,"uid":299436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"104fe79e07457c7ddfb5336c6c31c4e8e7f10aea","ti